sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant Booking as Booking Saga
    participant Inventory as Inventory Service
    participant Payment as Payment Service
    participant Notify as Notification Service
    participant Search as Search Index

    User->>Booking: POST /booking (idempotency_key)
    Booking->>Booking: Dedupe via idempotency key

    Note over Booking,Inventory: Step 1 - Reserve inventory (pessimistic lock)
    Booking->>Inventory: BEGIN; SELECT FOR UPDATE date rows
    alt Capacity available for all dates
        Inventory->>Inventory: UPDATE available_count -= 1
        Inventory-->>Booking: Reserved (commit)
    else Sold out
        Inventory-->>Booking: 409 Conflict
        Booking-->>User: No availability
    end

    Note over Booking,Payment: Step 2 - Charge payment
    Booking->>Payment: Charge(amount, idempotency_key)
    alt Payment succeeds
        Payment-->>Booking: payment_id
    else Payment fails
        Payment-->>Booking: Declined
        Booking->>Inventory: COMPENSATE: release inventory
        Booking-->>User: Booking failed
    end

    Note over Booking,Notify: Step 3 - Confirm
    Booking->>Booking: Persist booking record
    Booking-->>User: { booking_id, confirmed }
    Booking-)Notify: Send confirmation email (retry queue)

    Note over Inventory,Search: Async search sync
    Inventory-)Search: CDC -> reindex hotel doc (eventual)
